A tiny example
Here’s the shape of a basic app (not run here, since it needs a live server):
library(shiny)

ui &lt;- fluidPage(
  sliderInput("n", "Number of points", min = 10, max = 500, value = 100),
  plotOutput("plot")
)

server &lt;- function(input, output) {
  output$plot &lt;- renderPlot({
    hist(rnorm(input$n))   # updates whenever the slider moves
  })
}

shinyApp(ui, server)
